</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Tesla 擬採用 Apple AirPlay   改善車內音響播放質素</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/01/teala-apple-airplay/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=teala-apple-airplay</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[EMMA]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jun 2022 10:18:17 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1102634</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Tesla 近期推出的，新 Model 3 與 Model S 音響系統受許多評論家和購買者的好評，有人更認為音 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Tesla 近期推出的，新 Model 3 與 Model S 音響系統受許多評論家和購買者的好評，有人更認為音響效果堪比知名 B&amp;O 音響，可是在手機藍牙傳輸時音質卻不佳。近日，有 Tesla 創辦人 Elon Musk Twiter 回應網友，指正在考慮採用 Apple 的 AirPlay，從而改善車內藍牙傳輸時音響播放質素。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">I love that we can request a tesla feature and it might be added. Like this:The speaker system in Teslas are so good, but we are limited by the quality of Bluetooth. Could we have AirPlay added? It’s adds the ability for lossless streaming. The hardware necessary is already there</p><p>&mdash; ShibaDoge (@JacobB1290H) <a href="https://twitter.com/JacobB1290H/status/1529997326885871616?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">May 27, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>AirPlay 是 Apple 獨家無線影音串流播放技術，允許設備與設備影音之間傳輸。AirPlay 是使用 Wi-Fi 並非藍牙，而 Tesla 車內皆設有 Wi-Fi，因此 Musk 補充在硬件支援上不成問題，只要額外研發解決方案即可。</p><p>然而，如 Tesla 是次確實引入 Apple 的 AirPlay 將會是很大突破。因近年有許多 Tesla 用戶一直要求其電動汽車能引入 Apple 的 CarPlay 都未有實行，最終亦決定採用自家研發的的軟件生態系統。</p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">資料</span><span class="s2">來源：<a href="https://www.techtimes.com/articles/276139/20220531/teslas-elon-musk-adopt-apples-airplay-improved-sound-system-vehicles.htm">techtimes</a></span></p><p class="p1">—</p><p class="p2"><span class="s3">unwire.hk</span> Mewe <span class="s4">專頁：</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span class="s3">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=pSAX38ec0Ac:GODJj0yoySE:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=pSAX38ec0Ac:GODJj0yoySE:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>「高質」交友 app 成網民熱話　香港只有 5 間大學學生能加入</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/01/dating-app-workheart/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=dating-app-workheart</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[NatalieFu]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jun 2022 09:37:54 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[交友 App]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1102694</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>疫情下大家都不能外出，相信使用交友 app 已經成為不少人的生活習慣。近日臺灣一款新出的交友 app 「Wor [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>疫情下大家都不能外出，相信使用交友 app 已經成為不少人的生活習慣。近日臺灣一款新出的交友 app 「WorkHeart」，應用程式主打「高質交友」，系統會於註冊用戶時以學歷及公司作篩選，引起港臺兩地網民熱議。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1102695 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-01-at-5.06.22-PM-521x580.png" alt="" width="521" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-01-at-5.06.22-PM-521x580.png 521w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-01-at-5.06.22-PM-808x900.png 808w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-01-at-5.06.22-PM-768x855.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-01-at-5.06.22-PM.png 1180w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 521px" /></p><p>Workheart 主打「高品質白領交友」，用戶在註冊時必須使用學校或企業的電子郵箱進行驗證，系統會根據官方名單再作篩選，只有名單內的學校及公司才能獲批加入。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1102697 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-01-at-5.06.41-PM-694x537.png" alt="" width="694" height="537" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-01-at-5.06.41-PM-694x537.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-01-at-5.06.41-PM-1163x900.png 1163w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-01-at-5.06.41-PM-768x594.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-01-at-5.06.41-PM.png 1487w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>除臺灣以外，Workheart 現時開放予香港及新加坡的「高質」男女加入，現時香港只有 5 間大學能申請，包括香港大學、中文大學、科技大學、城市大學及理工大學。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1102708 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-01-at-5.21.27-PM-694x302.png" alt="" width="694" height="302" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-01-at-5.21.27-PM-694x302.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-01-at-5.21.27-PM-768x334.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-01-at-5.21.27-PM.png 790w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>而「高質公司」名單則包括 Big Four、3M、滙豐銀行、渣打銀行、Amazon、FaceBook 等跨國企業。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class=" wp-image-1102709 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-01-at-5.21.43-PM-213x580.png" alt="" width="253" height="689" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-01-at-5.21.43-PM-213x580.png 213w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-01-at-5.21.43-PM-331x900.png 331w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-01-at-5.21.43-PM.png 504w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 253px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1102710 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-01-at-5.21.53-PM-305x580.png" alt="" width="305" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-01-at-5.21.53-PM-305x580.png 305w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-01-at-5.21.53-PM-473x900.png 473w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-01-at-5.21.53-PM.png 490w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 305px" /></p><p>高質大學及企業名單亦在討論區上掀起網民熱議，有很多網民質疑用學歷及公司決定是否精英不合時宜。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="wp-image-1102698 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/1.png" alt="" width="489" height="313" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="wp-image-1102699 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/2.png" alt="" width="464" height="224" /></p><p>亦有網民不認同名單內的學校及企業是「精英」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="wp-image-1102700 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/5-694x339.png" alt="" width="475" height="232" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/5-694x339.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/5-768x375.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/5.png 884w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 475px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="wp-image-1102701 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/3-694x340.png" alt="" width="486" height="238" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/3-694x340.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/3.png 756w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 486px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="wp-image-1102702 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/4.png" alt="" width="458" height="246" /></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://udn.com/news/story/120912/6349626">聯合新聞網</a>、<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3023976/page/1">連登討論區</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
