</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Google 街景服務 15 週年，香港首個攝手 Raf：背住裝備行過香港 80% 山路</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/01/googlestreetview-2/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=googlestreetview-2</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jun 2022 07:59:59 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1102549</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Google 街景在 2007 年服務至今剛好 15 週年，而服務自 2010 年在香港推出亦都有十二年時間。 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Google 街景在 2007 年服務至今剛好 15 週年，而服務自 2010 年在香港推出亦都有十二年時間。Google 為慶祝服務 15 週年，在 Google 地圖加入彩蛋，更在香港邀請傳媒朋友參與盛典，訪問香港 Google 街景首位攝影師 Raf 分享他的寶貴經歷。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/L1014290-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102562" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/L1014290-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/L1014290-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/L1014290-1280x852.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/L1014290-768x511.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/L1014290-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/L1014290-2048x1363.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/L1014290-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Google 為慶祝街景服務提供 15 週年，在 Google Maps 加入兩個彩蛋，期間限定為 Google 嚮導角色「Pegman」換上生日造型，駕駛導航圖示加入限定街景車可供用戶選擇。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/JBjNGMkfwSuXtBixzFhdUH-970-80.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102552" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/JBjNGMkfwSuXtBixzFhdUH-970-80-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/JBjNGMkfwSuXtBixzFhdUH-970-80-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/JBjNGMkfwSuXtBixzFhdUH-970-80-768x433.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/JBjNGMkfwSuXtBixzFhdUH-970-80.jpg 970w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-19.20.03.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1102551" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-19.20.03.jpg" alt="" width="312" height="200" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/maxresdefault-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102553" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/maxresdefault-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/maxresdefault-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/maxresdefault-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/maxresdefault-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>目前 Google 街景服務已在全球過百個國家地區分享超過 2,200 億張街景 360 度實景照片。為令到街景服務繼續提升，新一代 Google 街景相機將會在明年投入拍攝工作當中。全新拍攝器材重量大幅減至 6.8kg，可穩定裝置於有車頂行李架的汽車上。其 LiDAR 光學雷達掃描儀，可更細緻捕捉道路標記及損毀的細節，模組式設計亦讓拍攝人員輕易地增減器材。拍攝時工作人員可透過手機操控器材，令拍攝過程更為順利。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/PXL_20220518_1749540681.max-1000x1000-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102554" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/PXL_20220518_1749540681.max-1000x1000-1-319x580.jpg" alt="" width="319" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/PXL_20220518_1749540681.max-1000x1000-1-319x580.jpg 319w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/PXL_20220518_1749540681.max-1000x1000-1-494x900.jpg 494w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/PXL_20220518_1749540681.max-1000x1000-1.jpg 512w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 319px" /></a></p><p>而 Google 街景時光機亦快將會加入 iOS/Android 手機版支援。現時用戶已可在電腦網頁版上，打開街景時回顧此地的舊日景色。</p><p>日後 Google 街景會加入新功能「3D 沉浸式地圖」，在觀賞街景時，用戶可時放大街道上店鋪的細節，猶如親臨其景。此服務最初會在洛杉磯、倫敦、紐約、三藩市、東京推出，將逐步擴展至更多城市。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4360-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102559" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4360-694x421.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="421" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4360-694x421.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4360-1280x777.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4360-768x466.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4360-1536x932.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4360-2048x1243.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4360-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4357-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102558" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4357-694x416.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="416" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4357-694x416.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4357-1280x767.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4357-768x460.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4357-1536x921.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4357-2048x1227.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4357-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>香港首位街景操作員：香港 8 成山路我都行過</h2><p>今日 Google 邀請本地傳媒參與 Street View 15 週年盛典，請來了香港第一位街景操作員何文豐（Raf）分享經驗。其實除了城市中的街景之外，「街景」服務也包含了山路、只供行人步行的道路。Raf 就說香港大約 80% 的山路他也走過了，包括香港四徑－－麥理浩徑、衛奕信徑、鳳凰徑、港島徑，還有離島的山路，但有一次行山路的痛苦經歷，當時他走一段 9 公里的山路到一半，發現前路的天色不對，需要馬上離開。改天他與同事一同背住 18kg 的裝備，從頭開始走過整條路段。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4382-1-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102561" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4382-1-694x421.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="421" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4382-1-694x421.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4382-1-1280x776.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4382-1-768x466.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4382-1-1536x932.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4382-1-2048x1242.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4382-1-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4349-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102560" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4349-694x432.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="432" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4349-694x432.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4349-1280x796.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4349-768x478.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4349-1536x956.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4349-2048x1274.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4349-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4372.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102556" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4372-694x460.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="460" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4372-694x460.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4372-1280x849.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4372-768x509.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4372-1536x1019.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IMG_4372.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>有一次較為難忘的經歷，就是駕駛著裝有大件攝影器材的汽車，在狹窄的道路中遇到有牛隻吃草，他當時沒有驅趕牠們，打開自己的飯盒跟牛隻一齊開餐，等候牠們離開。</p><p>Raf 又分享其實每次拍攝街景，自己都未能享受這些街景、景色，需要每一刻都留意、操作拍攝器材，又或者專心駕駛、行走既定的路線等。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-19.49.14.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1102550" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-19.49.14-694x433.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="433" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-19.49.14-694x433.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-19.49.14-768x480.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-31-19.49.14.jpg 1209w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有不少街景是山路，需要靠人具著拍攝裝置上山拍攝，圖為金山郊野公園家樂徑</p><p>Raf 認為香港好多地貌都變得好快，例如尖沙咀新世界中心、觀塘裕民坊等，現在只可以靠 Google 街景時光機功能，回顧當日景色。</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write